00:03:04.440 --> 00:03:06.520
Saya harus menjawabnya, Tuan Jindal.

00:03:14.840 --> 00:03:16.680
Media berpikir

00:03:16.880 --> 00:03:19.520
ketika dua orang berdiri
di sisi yang berlawanan

00:03:19.600 --> 00:03:21.520
